flowchart TD
  Upload[User Uploads Image / Video / Audio] --> Raw[S3 RawMediaBucket]
  Raw --> Dispatcher[Lambda Dispatcher]
  Dispatcher --> SFN[Step Functions Workflow]
  SFN --> Prep[Prepare Metadata]
  SFN --> RekImg[Rekognition Image Labels + Faces]
  SFN --> RekVid[Rekognition Video Label Detection]
  SFN --> Transcribe[Amazon Transcribe]
  SFN --> Comprehend[Amazon Comprehend NLP]
  RekImg --> Inter[S3 Intermediate JSON]
  RekVid --> Inter
  Transcribe --> Transcript[S3 Transcript JSON]
  Comprehend --> Inter
  SFN --> Finalize[Aggregate + Safe Review Flags]
  Finalize --> Final[S3 Final Results]
  Finalize --> DDB[DynamoDB Metadata Index]
